<html>
<head>
  <title>Order Completion Notification</title>
</head>
<body style='font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333;'>
  <div style='max-width: 600px; margin: auto; border: 1px solid #eaeaea; padding: 20px;'>
    <!-- Header with Larger Logo -->
    <div style='text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;'>
      <img src='https://task-trek.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/QuickQuest.png' alt='QuickQuest Logo' style='max-width: 300px; margin-bottom: 10px;' />
      <h2 style='color: #4FB8B3;'>Order Completion Notification</h2>
    </div>
    <!-- Greeting -->
    <p>Dear {{customerName}},</p>
    <p>We are pleased to inform you that your order has been completed:</p>
    <!-- Job ID and Details -->
    <div style='background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px;'>
      <h3 style='color: #4FB8B3;'>Completed Job Details</h3>
      <p><strong>Job ID:</strong> {{orderID}}</p>
      <p><strong>Service:</strong> {{serviceName}}</p>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> {{description}}</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong> ${{price}}</p>
      <p><strong>Date Ordered:</strong> {{orderedDate}}</p>
      <p><strong>Worker:</strong> {{workerName}}</p>
    </div>
    <!-- Feedback -->
    <div style='margin-bottom: 20px;'>
      <p>We hope you had a great experience with our service. If you have any feedback or concerns, please let us know.</p>
    </div>
    <!-- Leave a Review -->
    <div style='text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;'>
      <p>Leave a review and let us know how we did!</p>
      <a href='https://quickquest.com/review' style='display: inline-block; background-color: #4FB8B3; color: #fff; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;'>Leave a Review</a>
    </div>
    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer style='text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;'>
      <p>Thank you for choosing QuickQuest. We appreciate your business and look forward to serving you again in the future.</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>